<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA27">
<l>ārē tuyaruḻantār tuṉpuṟṟā rāṇṭaiyār</l>
<l>kārē malinta karuṅkaṭalai – nērē</l>
<l>kaṭaintāṉaik kāraṇaṉai nīraṇaimēṟ paḷḷi</l>
<l>yaṭaintāṉai nāḷu maṭaintu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who are those who have borne misery, where are those who have experienced sorrow</l>
<l>after daily approaching the one who takes</l>
<l>rest on the water bed, the cause, the one who directly</l>
<l>churned the black sea abounding in clouds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
